settings.question: Are your shoes vegan?
settings.answer:
Conzuri shoes are vegan-friendly, excluding designs from our smart range.

The formal collection currently does not include vegan options due to our focus on traditional craftsmanship and materials that meet our stringent durability and aesthetic standards.

We are actively exploring high-quality, sustainable vegan materials and hope to expand our offerings in the future.

settings.question: What are the materials used in your shoes?
settings.answer:
Our collection is crafted from a variety of high-grade materials, including durable leather, plush suede, and advanced synthetic fabrics (chosen for their exceptional quality and performance).

For detailed information on each shoe's construction, we encourage you to explore the product descriptions on our website.

settings.question: Can I cancel my order?
settings.answer:
We accept cancellations that are initiated within 6 hours of ordering. If orders have already been fulfilled at any point, we are unable to process a cancellation. 


Once items are in-transit, you will have to wait for your order to be delivered and return the item once it has been received.

Email HERE to request cancellation

settings.question: How can I change my order?
settings.answer:
If you ordered the wrong size, or design - please reach out to us HERE

We can not reverse fulfilment once our shipping team have dealt with your order, so if you fail to email our support team in-time, we may not be able to change it for you.

settings.question: Exchanges & re-delivery
settings.answer:
If your package was returned due to an "incomplete address" - you will be charged a re-delivery fee to re-route the package back to your correct location. 

If you want to exchange the item you have received, you will have to return the product to our closest warehouse location.

Depending on the cirucmstance, you may not have to pay for the product again, but you will be responsible for your own return costs and are subject to a re-delivery fee.

settings.question: Will I get charged customs tax?
settings.answer:
In 99% of cases, you will not be charged customs tax.

In the scanario that you are charged - please reach out to our support team HERE

settings.question: I haven't received any cofirmation emails?
settings.answer:
You should recieve a confirmation email immediately after purchase. 

Please wait five minutes in case there have been server-side deliverability issues.

Please check your junk folder too. 

It could be that you have entered your email incorrectly, so just get in touch to double-check and we can change your details accordingly. 

Contact Us

settings.question: I haven't received my tracking information?
settings.answer:
You should recieve your tracking information as soon as your order has been fulfilled.

Orders are fulfilled within 24-48 hours (Monday-Friday)

If you have recieved previous emails from us, then your email isn't the problem - so get in touch with us HERE for further assistance. 

If you haven't received any emails from us at all, you should also get in touch to double-check your details are correct.

settings.question: My tacking information hasn't updated?
settings.answer:
Out tracking platform may take some time to reflect updates on your order, so we advise leaving at least 3 days before seeing fulilment progress.

There may sometimes be delays beyond our control, but if your order has been shipped - it will get to you. 

If you have any concerns, you can always contact us HERE for updates.

settings.question: My discount code doesn't work?
settings.answer:
Get in touch with us HERE to let us know the code you are trying to use and we will do our best to assist.

Some promotional codes have set expiry-dates, depending on the promotion received.

Be sure to check your email/SMS for any "limited time" wording.

settings.question: My card isn't working?
settings.answer:
We accept most credit and debit cards, so there shouldn't be a problem on our end. 

Of course, we would advise double-checking your balance and details before reaching out to us.


We also have fraud prevention in place, so if your address details do not match your billing details - this can sometimes flag up on our system.

If you cannot purchase with your card, try purchasging with PayPal if applicable.


For any further assistance, please reach out HERE

settings.question: It says you don't deliver to my country?
settings.answer:
We ship to most countries across the world, excluding remote areas that have higher-risk of delivery failure.

Customer experience is important to us and we do not want to accept orders that would take a long time to arrive.

There are also certain products that are only available to US customers, as they are shipped directly from our US warehouse.

Unfortunately we do not have the resources to ship internationally from this facility just yet.
